      "content": "i see. it feels like the \"innovation\" argument sounds a bit like they're just trying to avoid accountability. if we're talking about the literal survival of the species, is it even possible to have a \"balanced\" debate between economic growth and extinction? or is the risk just too real to treat it as a fiveo-fifty thing?",
